# Problem Statement – Live Text Preview (DOM Mini Project)

Create a simple web page where a user can type something in an input box and see that text displayed instantly on the screen.

---

## Requirements

1. There should be:
   - One input box
   - One heading (h1)
   - One button (Clear)

2. When the user types in the input box:
   - The same text should appear in the heading in real-time

3. When the user clicks the Clear button:
   - The input box should become empty
   - The heading should reset to default text
     (Example: "Your text will appear here")

## Example

User types: `Hello`
Output shows: `Hello`

User clicks Clear
Output resets

---

## Difficulty Level

Beginner
Perfect for practicing basic DOM concepts

---
